Package com.rubynaxela.kyanite.util

Class Colors

java.lang.Object
com.rubynaxela.kyanite.graphics.Colors
public class Colors extends Object
This class provides a library of pre-defined colors from the CSS language.

      @NotNull @Contract(pure=true) public static @NotNull Color opacity(@NotNull @NotNull Color color, float opacity)
      Returns the specified color with the specified alpha (opacity) value.
      Parameters:
      color - a color
      opacity - the color's opacity value ranging between 0.0f (fully transparent) and 1.0f (fully opaque)
      Returns:
      the specified color with the specified opacity

    • darker

      @NotNull @Contract(pure=true, value="_ -> new") public static @NotNull Color darker(@NotNull @NotNull Color color)
      Returns a color darker than the specified color. Each component of the resulting color is the corresponding component of the original color divided by two.
      Parameters:
      color - a color
      Returns:
      a color darker than the specified color

    • brighter

      @NotNull @Contract(pure=true, value="_ -> new") public static @NotNull Color brighter(@NotNull @NotNull Color color)
      Returns a color brighter than the specified color. Each component of the resulting color is the arithmetic mean of the corresponding component of the original color and 255.
      Parameters:
      color - a color
      Returns:
      a color brighter than the specified color
